metadata.name: Moonlight over the Mediterranean Sea
metadata.description:
#1 NFT + sending the Original Canvas Painting to the NFT owner.

size: 100 x 100 cm 
Acrylic, spray paint and art putty on canvas. Textured painting.

When I admire the moon I have a feeling of tranquility, relaxation and harmony. It is these feelings that I have transferred onto the canvas. An atmosphere of silence and tranquility that evokes meditation. The moon's path away from the shore on which I am standing is like a bridge over which I can come to mental harmony.
